incident_updates.body: Start time : 09/01/2023 08:00 UTC End time : 09/01/2023 18:00 UTC Service impact : Delivery and reset of Managed Kubernetes clusters v1.22 disabled Ongoing actions : Following our end-of-support policy, the Managed Kubernetes Service team will mark as deprecated the Kubernetes version 1.22. It will no longer be possible to create Managed Kubernetes clusters under the 1.22 version, or to reset existing clusters into this version. For more details, please refer to these documentations: https://docs.ovh.com/gb/en/kubernetes/eos-eol-policies/ https://docs.ovh.com/gb/en/kubernetes/kubernetes-plugins-software-versions-reserved-resources/
